Package: robarma
Type: Package
Title: R Wrapper for RobARMA
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Kusti", family = "Aholainen", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "kusti.aholainen@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Kusti Aholainen <kusti.aholainen@gmail.com>
Description: R interface to the RobARMA C++ library providing robust and classical
    ARMA estimation methods (OLS, MLE, S, MM, BIP-MM, filtered tau) and simulation.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: Rcpp
Suggests: testthat
Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements: Ceres Solver (>= 2.0), Eigen3 (>= 3.4), glog, gflags
    (macOS: brew install ceres-solver eigen;
     Linux: libceres-dev libeigen3-dev libgoogle-glog-dev libgflags-dev)
